===Noun===
'''growl''' ([[growls]])

#The deep, threatening sound made by a [[surly]] dog; a [[grumbling]] sound.

====Translations====
*Polish: [[warczenie]]

===Verb===

'''to growl'''

#To utter a deep guttural sound, as an angry dog; to give forth an angry, grumbling sound.
#To express by growling.

